Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.54,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}問いかけてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:45.59,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}もう夏の終わり
