Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.66,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}スピード増してく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:14.54,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}秋色の雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:24.25,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}この頬に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:30.22,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}触れるその髪が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:36.64,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}とても愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:42.15,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}とても切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:49.03,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}離れたくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:17:00.21,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}ねぇ　探してる　見つけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:06.00,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}形のない何かを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:11.97,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}人はカタチを見せるのが得意なの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:18.60,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}遠い記憶青い母のように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:24.61,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}波のないお日様の中
