Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:31.29,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}拂过水面的忧郁微风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.54,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}试着轻声询问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:45.59,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}夏日已近尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:59.86,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}日渐西沉的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.66,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}也加快了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:14.54,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}秋色的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:24.25,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}轻抚脸颊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:30.22,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}是你的发丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:36.64,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此惹人怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:42.15,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此令人伤怀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:49.03,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我不愿与你分离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:17:00.21,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我在追寻 渴望找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:06.00,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}那无形无影之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:11.97,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}人们总擅长展现自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:18.60,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}记忆太过遥远 就像大海一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:24.61,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}阳光下风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:34.24,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}似那浅眠的鸟儿 归去吧
